				\begin{document}$$s_t$$\end{document}st. Through episodes of consecutive actions, neural-network weights are updated, optimizing policies to maximize expected rewards. For recent advances in flow control using MARL, interested readers are directed to Belus et al. (2019), Brunton et al. (2015), Vignon et al. (2023), where significant progress and insights have been reported.

